{"tid":2380143,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[單車L] 有冇人鍾意踩單速車多過變速車","createTime":"2021-01-25T16:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T16:28:37.000Z","uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a334e518e99705a0cb0ca6a46f38bf6a28ee7b69","tid":2380143,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊Fixed Gear<br />\n<br />\n平時踩21波以上嘅MTB，發現自己來來去去都係踩中餅嗰兩三個波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />主要係上落大斜先轉<br />\n但係個變速器就成日壞，又甩鍊又剩，打理好麻煩<br />\n<br />\n反而自己踩架單速16吋細摺仲開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />簡單，廢柴如我唔使諗咁多<br />\n腳力直接換速度<br />\n車身輕所以上斜唔算辛苦，大斜就抽車，基本上香港大部份路都頂到<br />\n大架嘅復古單速車又型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度有冇單速車同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7f2bce7c5dbb550b3e8843ec7d7d878ecd346c","tid":2380143,"uid":155732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"從來冇甩過鍊<br />\n亂轉波先甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501733bf4b5dae78e9870fb934129ea4c592b5ff","tid":2380143,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be7f2bce7c5dbb550b3e8843ec7d7d878ecd346c","tid":2380143,"uid":155732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"從來冇甩過鍊<br />\n亂轉波先甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"我甩鍊通常3波變咗1波<br />\n落多一波就甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}